==================================================================================================================================================
POST http://REGEX(.*)/notify?subscriptionId=urn:S2
Content-Length: 233
User-Agent: orionld/REGEX(.*)
Host: REGEX(.*)
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Link: <https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/v1/ngsi-ld-core-contextREGEX(.*)
