Ngsild-Attribute-Format: Normalized

{
    "data": [
        {
            "deletedAt": "202REGEX(.*)Z",
            "id": "urn:E1",
            "type": "T"
        }
    ],
    "id": "urn:ngsi-ld:Notification:REGEX(.*)",
    "notifiedAt": "202REGEX(.*)Z",
    "subscriptionId": "urn:S1",
    "type": "Notification"
}
=======================================


--TEARDOWN--
brokerStop CB
dbDrop CB
accumulatorStop
